title: Moldovan PM hands grand prize in winemaking sector on National Wine Day (Government of Moldova) ...
text: ( Source : Government of Moldova ) Prime Minister Valeriu Strelet today participated in an event dedicated to National Wine Day, carried out at the Asconi winery in Puhoi village, Ialoveni district . The event was marked at other ten wineries
